{"word":"νεωστί","slug":"νεωστί","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>νεωστί</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>adverb of <a href='S:νέος'><el>νέος</el></a>, for <a href='S:νέως'><el>νέως</el></a>, as <a href='S:μεγαλωστί'><el>μεγαλωστί</el></a> for <a href='S:μεγάλως'><el>μεγάλως</el></a>\n<p/><i>lately, just now</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}